00:27:21.520 --> 00:27:23.430
a resort.

00:27:23.440 --> 00:27:25.950
As I was looking into

00:27:25.960 --> 00:27:26.830
it,

00:27:26.840 --> 00:27:29.430
I could see a great

00:27:29.440 --> 00:27:31.870
revival coming—all kinds of things when

00:27:31.880 --> 00:27:34.110
I was looking into Cuba last night.

00:27:34.120 --> 00:27:36.910
It looked like a

00:27:36.920 --> 00:27:39.190
blessing for the Cuban people.

00:27:41.240 --> 00:27:44.590
Then I was praying into

00:27:45.880 --> 00:27:47.310
California,

00:27:47.320 --> 00:27:50.150
and the Lord said, 'Do you

00:27:50.150 --> 00:27:50.160
see?'When

00:27:50.160 --> 00:27:52.870
I paused there, I could see California

00:27:52.880 --> 00:27:55.230
and I could see the people of California

00:27:55.240 --> 00:27:57.750
were fed up with Gavin,

00:27:57.760 --> 00:28:00.070
were fed up with the way their politics

00:28:00.080 --> 00:28:02.430
are going. As we

00:28:02.440 --> 00:28:04.630
uncover all this

00:28:04.640 --> 00:28:08.030
great fraud, I saw the people of

00:28:08.040 --> 00:28:10.870
California becoming

00:28:10.880 --> 00:28:12.550
outraged,

00:28:12.560 --> 00:28:15.590
saying 'enough is

00:28:15.590 --> 00:28:15.600
enough.'And

00:28:15.600 --> 00:28:18.550
the Lord said, 'Pray into this: a

00:28:18.560 --> 00:28:23.270
red wave of political shaking that would

00:28:23.280 --> 00:28:27.110
shake the United States and the world

00:28:27.120 --> 00:28:31.310
for a red wave that would try to come

00:28:31.320 --> 00:28:33.150
over California,

00:28:33.160 --> 00:28:37.310
flipping the governor to a Republican,

00:28:37.320 --> 00:28:42.390
flipping seats into the Republican

00:28:42.390 --> 00:28:42.400
House.'Like

00:28:42.400 --> 00:28:45.190
Nancy Pelosi,

00:28:45.200 --> 00:28:47.630
bye-bye.

00:28:47.640 --> 00:28:52.190
A new wave of red trying to spring forth

00:28:52.200 --> 00:28:53.870
out of California. Now, I'm not saying

00:28:53.880 --> 00:28:55.150
all of it,

00:28:55.160 --> 00:29:00.630
but I saw red like it was painted red

00:29:00.640 --> 00:29:02.110
across California. And the Lord said,

00:29:02.120 --> 00:29:03.550
'Pray into

00:29:03.550 --> 00:29:03.560
that.'There's

00:29:03.560 --> 00:29:05.590
much more

00:29:05.600 --> 00:29:09.270
corruption that needs to be uncovered

00:29:09.280 --> 00:29:11.950
concerning this to bring the people into

00:29:11.950 --> 00:29:11.960
enlightenment

00:29:11.960 --> 00:29:14.230
and

00:29:14.240 --> 00:29:16.670
being enraged that

00:29:16.670 --> 00:29:16.680
they've

00:29:16.680 --> 00:29:18.670
been played.

00:29:18.680 --> 00:29:21.350
But the Lord said it's the same

00:29:21.360 --> 00:29:23.350
over Minnesota.

00:29:23.360 --> 00:29:27.870
Pray for a red wave over Minnesota,

00:29:27.880 --> 00:29:31.710
for a rising up of people who are fed

00:29:31.720 --> 00:29:37.630
up.

00:29:37.640 --> 00:29:40.630
I can still see going into

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:42.710
November; I was

00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:46.070
praying into the election.

00:29:46.080 --> 00:29:48.390
The Lord said, 'You can win the

00:29:48.390 --> 00:29:48.400
Senate.'I

00:29:48.400 --> 00:29:50.990
saw it won by one.

00:29:51.000 --> 00:29:53.750
I was praying

00:29:53.760 --> 00:29:57.350
to keep it Republican

00:29:57.360 --> 00:29:59.470
by praying in the right

00:29:59.480 --> 00:30:02.670
leaders, and I saw one seat.

00:30:02.680 --> 00:30:05.430
Then I saw the House, and the Lord said,

00:30:05.440 --> 00:30:07.990
'You can pray this,'and I saw the House

00:30:08.000 --> 00:30:10.590
staying

00:30:10.590 --> 00:30:10.600
by

00:30:10.600 --> 00:30:12.070
more than 20

00:30:12.080 --> 00:30:13.630
seats.

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:16.750
I saw the number 20. Remember 20?

00:30:16.760 --> 00:30:18.870
What was that about again? I saw

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:21.510
20. Was that something personal?

00:30:23.680 --> 00:30:24.910
Yes, it was.

00:30:24.920 --> 00:30:27.390
I've seen so much lately;

00:30:27.400 --> 00:30:30.830
that was something else.

00:30:30.830 --> 00:30:30.840
So,

00:30:30.840 --> 00:30:34.590
forgive me. I bring

00:30:34.600 --> 00:30:36.790
personal things in,

00:30:46.480 --> 00:30:48.470
but it all has to do with the same

00:30:48.480 --> 00:30:51.590
thing,

00:30:51.590 --> 00:30:51.600
doesn't

00:30:51.600 --> 00:30:53.990
it?

00:30:54.000 --> 00:30:57.070
Praying into the

00:30:57.070 --> 00:30:57.080
20.

00:30:57.080 --> 00:31:00.430
I keep praying into these things that the

00:31:00.430 --> 00:31:00.440
Lord is

00:31:00.440 --> 00:31:01.750
talking to me

00:31:01.750 --> 00:31:01.760
about—my

00:31:01.760 --> 00:31:03.230
personal ministry,

00:31:04.560 --> 00:31:06.950
the time

00:31:06.960 --> 00:31:08.550
frames of things,

00:31:08.550 --> 00:31:08.560
and

00:31:08.560 --> 00:31:11.110
praying

00:31:11.110 --> 00:31:11.120
for

00:31:11.120 --> 00:31:13.350
President Trump because he said he's

00:31:13.360 --> 00:31:16.230
tired.

00:31:16.240 --> 00:31:18.550
He needs help. And that's

00:31:18.550 --> 00:31:18.560
why

00:31:18.560 --> 00:31:20.070
I tried to tell you all—I wasn't

00:31:20.080 --> 00:31:22.830
trying to pick at him last night,

00:31:22.840 --> 00:31:25.190
but I'm going to tell you, you must pray

00:31:25.200 --> 00:31:26.590
for him.

00:31:31.360 --> 00:31:34.590
He won't make it without our prayers.

00:31:38.880 --> 00:31:40.990
It gets to the point

00:31:41.000 --> 00:31:42.630
where you all need to

00:31:42.640 --> 00:31:44.390
have discernment for yourselves. You need

00:31:44.400 --> 00:31:46.590
to hear God for yourself, but you need

00:31:46.600 --> 00:31:49.350
to filter it with the Word.

00:31:49.360 --> 00:31:52.790
Everything you are hearing

00:31:52.800 --> 00:31:55.070
and how you

00:31:55.080 --> 00:31:57.350
try to correct me—filter it with the

00:31:57.360 --> 00:31:59.630
Scripture.

00:31:59.640 --> 00:32:02.670
Pray about our nation. Pray for us to be

00:32:02.680 --> 00:32:05.230
a sheep nation. Pray for us to stay and

00:32:05.240 --> 00:32:08.910
have a great revival.

00:32:08.920 --> 00:32:11.990
Pray for a shaking and

00:32:11.990 --> 00:32:12.000
awakening

00:32:12.000 --> 00:32:15.030
in the churches.

00:32:15.040 --> 00:32:16.430
But when you're praying and

00:32:16.440 --> 00:32:18.750
seeing into things,

00:32:18.760 --> 00:32:21.270
like I said, we

00:32:21.280 --> 00:32:23.910
see in part and hear in part. You

00:32:23.920 --> 00:32:26.790
think things are right

00:32:26.790 --> 00:32:26.800
here—it

00:32:26.800 --> 00:32:28.150
looks like it's

00:32:28.160 --> 00:32:30.070
right on your nose—but yet it's just a

00:32:30.080 --> 00:32:32.150
couple years out. It could be a little

00:32:32.160 --> 00:32:33.470
further out than what you

00:32:33.480 --> 00:32:36.470
think. Because in our natural mind, we

00:32:36.480 --> 00:32:38.030
don't understand the spirit realm when

00:32:38.040 --> 00:32:40.790
it comes to time.

00:32:40.800 --> 00:32:42.830
God's vast. There is no beginning and

00:32:42.840 --> 00:32:45.550
there is no end. So His timing

00:32:45.560 --> 00:32:47.270
of when He says something's

00:32:47.270 --> 00:32:47.280
coming—and

00:32:47.280 --> 00:32:49.830
you say, 'Soon, Brandon, when is

00:32:49.830 --> 00:32:49.840
soon?'—soon

00:32:49.840 --> 00:32:54.150
to God could be 10 years,

00:32:54.160 --> 00:32:56.870
20 years,

00:32:56.870 --> 00:32:56.880
or

00:32:56.880 --> 00:32:59.150
a lot of things. But

00:32:59.160 --> 00:33:01.110
you don't try to add to or

00:33:01.120 --> 00:33:04.390
take away from anything you hear or see.

00:33:04.400 --> 00:33:07.230
I deliver it as I see it.

00:33:09.000 --> 00:33:11.350
To

00:33:11.360 --> 00:33:13.510
add a time frame to it would be really

00:33:13.520 --> 00:33:15.910
stupid.

00:33:15.920 --> 00:33:17.870
To say,

00:33:17.880 --> 00:33:19.950
'Well, this is my opinion'—who cares

00:33:19.960 --> 00:33:22.710
about Brandon Biggs's opinion?

00:33:22.720 --> 00:33:25.150
I'm just as flawed as you all are. Everybody

00:33:25.150 --> 00:33:25.160
has

00:33:25.160 --> 00:33:28.430
issues.

00:33:28.440 --> 00:33:29.790
I don't exalt

00:33:29.800 --> 00:33:31.190
myself above anything. That's what I'm

00:33:31.200 --> 00:33:33.310
telling you all. I'm just human.

00:33:33.320 --> 00:33:34.790
I have issues I'm

00:33:34.800 --> 00:33:37.310
overcoming just like you all do.

00:33:39.600 --> 00:33:41.430
I'm just a person

00:33:41.440 --> 00:33:44.030
used just like you all are.

00:33:44.040 --> 00:33:45.830
Regardless, this channel and everything has

00:33:45.840 --> 00:33:48.990
just been God's grace.

00:33:49.000 --> 00:33:50.630
Everybody has something we're working

00:33:50.640 --> 00:33:52.510
through. Everyone has something

00:33:52.520 --> 00:33:54.590
that you're seeking Him

00:33:56.040 --> 00:33:57.390
for—healing,

00:33:59.280 --> 00:34:01.950
finances, protection, whatever it may

00:34:01.960 --> 00:34:03.590
be.

00:34:03.600 --> 00:34:05.470
But we work out our salvation with fear

00:34:05.480 --> 00:34:07.110
and trembling.

00:34:07.120 --> 00:34:08.510
That's what I try to

00:34:08.520 --> 00:34:10.149
tell you all: when you get real

00:34:10.159 --> 00:34:12.350
with God, God will become real to you. I

00:34:12.360 --> 00:34:15.149
get tired of all the celebrity

00:34:17.440 --> 00:34:20.190
charismatic Christian stuff;

00:34:20.200 --> 00:34:23.669
it is over the top.

00:34:23.679 --> 00:34:25.430
When you talk

00:34:25.440 --> 00:34:27.470
to people and they're real with you,

00:34:27.480 --> 00:34:29.389
they are just as

00:34:29.399 --> 00:34:31.629
real. They go through things just

00:34:31.639 --> 00:34:33.909
like you do.

00:34:40.080 --> 00:34:43.190
We're all a work in progress.

00:34:45.280 --> 00:34:47.230
Humble yourselves underneath

00:34:47.240 --> 00:34:49.190
the mighty hand of God. Humble yourself.

00:34:49.200 --> 00:34:50.990
That's the bottom line. There is so much

00:34:51.000 --> 00:34:53.270
spiritual pride,

00:34:53.280 --> 00:34:55.389
and I see it all the time. A lot of

00:34:55.399 --> 00:34:58.870
arrogant people, and you go,

00:34:58.880 --> 00:35:01.150
'Hold on a minute. Don't you realize

00:35:01.160 --> 00:35:02.990
that I walk in a seer's

00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:05.590
anointing, and I can see all your mess,

00:35:05.600 --> 00:35:08.070
and I never tell anyone

00:35:08.070 --> 00:35:08.080
anything?

00:35:08.080 --> 00:35:10.390
I see the mess on a lot of people that

00:35:10.400 --> 00:35:12.830
think they have a lot going on for them.

00:35:12.840 --> 00:35:14.470
Some of them are on TV, and I look at them

00:35:14.480 --> 00:35:16.430
and go, 'But the Lord reveals everything

00:35:16.440 --> 00:35:18.230
about your business to tell me to pray

00:35:18.240 --> 00:35:19.510
for you.'He says, 'Listen, don't be like

00:35:19.520 --> 00:35:22.070
that.

00:35:22.080 --> 00:35:23.510
Humble yourself,

00:35:23.510 --> 00:35:23.520
Brandon.

00:35:23.520 --> 00:35:28.550
Remember the

00:35:28.550 --> 00:35:28.560
janitor.'It's

00:35:28.560 --> 00:35:31.030
interesting as a watchman

00:35:31.030 --> 00:35:31.040
because

00:35:31.040 --> 00:35:32.790
I see things that nobody else will

00:35:32.800 --> 00:35:35.910
see because the Lord allows me to.

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:37.830
Then he shows me things about myself

00:35:37.840 --> 00:35:40.110
all the time, and I

00:35:40.120 --> 00:35:41.870
don't even feel worthy to do

00:35:41.880 --> 00:35:43.430
anything. Some days I

00:35:43.430 --> 00:35:43.440
say,

00:35:43.440 --> 00:35:45.470
'God, thank God it's all by your

00:35:45.470 --> 00:35:45.480
grace,'but

00:35:45.480 --> 00:35:47.750
it really sets the stage

00:35:47.760 --> 00:35:50.310
for me to realize it has nothing to do

00:35:50.320 --> 00:35:52.950
with you

00:35:52.950 --> 00:35:52.960
and

00:35:52.960 --> 00:35:54.310
everything to do with how good

00:35:54.320 --> 00:35:55.950
God is

00:35:55.960 --> 00:35:57.870
and how merciful he is that he would

00:35:57.880 --> 00:36:00.310
even look in my direction.

00:36:00.320 --> 00:36:03.150
It's all by his grace. I

00:36:03.150 --> 00:36:03.160
said,

00:36:03.160 --> 00:36:05.310
'God, thank you for using

00:36:05.320 --> 00:36:08.910
somebody like

00:36:08.910 --> 00:36:08.920
me.'The

00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:11.110
other

00:36:11.110 --> 00:36:11.120
night—I

00:36:11.120 --> 00:36:12.830
try to explain this all the time—I don't

00:36:12.840 --> 00:36:17.310
know if he's going to show up tonight.

00:36:17.320 --> 00:36:20.590
I don't control it.

00:36:20.600 --> 00:36:22.150
Sometimes people want you to

00:36:22.160 --> 00:36:24.110
snap your fingers and

00:36:24.120 --> 00:36:25.510
think you control it and make this

00:36:25.520 --> 00:36:26.550
happen.

00:36:26.560 --> 00:36:29.670
But I can't control any of it.

00:36:29.680 --> 00:36:33.310
I am yielded to him.

00:36:34.480 --> 00:36:36.070
I'm just here.

00:36:36.080 --> 00:36:38.150
If you choose to use me again, fine.

00:36:38.160 --> 00:36:40.030
But

00:36:40.040 --> 00:36:41.270
I don't know how long I'll be

00:36:41.280 --> 00:36:43.710
doing this

00:36:43.720 --> 00:36:46.630
because I don't control any of it.

00:36:46.640 --> 00:36:49.270
He could say, 'I'm done

00:36:49.270 --> 00:36:49.280
tomorrow,'and

00:36:49.280 --> 00:36:50.350
I'll be there saying, 'Well, okay.

00:36:51.760 --> 00:36:52.830
I'll go back to selling on eBay

00:36:52.830 --> 00:36:52.840
and

00:36:52.840 --> 00:36:54.990
Poshmark full-time, really hitting

00:36:54.990 --> 00:36:55.000
it

00:36:55.000 --> 00:36:56.470
hard, trying to find

00:36:56.480 --> 00:36:59.750
things to

00:36:59.760 --> 00:37:01.990
flip.'Diana

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:03.750
does it now, but I used to help

00:37:03.760 --> 00:37:04.910
her with the measurements.

00:37:04.910 --> 00:37:04.920
I'd

00:37:04.920 --> 00:37:07.110
sit there for hours

00:37:07.120 --> 00:37:08.510
and measure all the clothes

00:37:08.520 --> 00:37:09.950
for the people

00:37:09.950 --> 00:37:09.960
because

00:37:09.960 --> 00:37:11.990
they always want to return them. eBay's

00:37:12.000 --> 00:37:14.750
return policy is terrible;

00:37:14.760 --> 00:37:16.150
you have to measure all the armpits and

00:37:16.160 --> 00:37:17.350
tell everybody if there's a stain.

00:37:17.360 --> 00:37:18.430
That

00:37:18.440 --> 00:37:19.750
was my job.

00:37:19.760 --> 00:37:21.630
Now Diana does that by herself, bless

00:37:21.640 --> 00:37:26.430
her heart. But

00:37:26.440 --> 00:37:28.030
it is what it is.

00:37:28.040 --> 00:37:29.190
I just want to tell you, that's

00:37:29.200 --> 00:37:30.870
why I try to say I'll pastor

00:37:30.880 --> 00:37:32.510
and I'll teach you all prayer and do what

00:37:32.520 --> 00:37:34.190
God's called me to do until he tells

00:37:34.200 --> 00:37:35.670
me to do something else. Whenever he

00:37:35.680 --> 00:37:37.910
told me about praying and having

00:37:37.920 --> 00:37:40.150
a theater in Branson, I didn't know

00:37:40.160 --> 00:37:42.150
when I would do it.

00:37:42.160 --> 00:37:44.670
I priced them; they're high dollar,

00:37:44.680 --> 00:37:47.070
millions of dollars.

00:37:47.080 --> 00:37:49.150
So you go, 'Okay, what does

00:37:49.160 --> 00:37:50.910
ministry look like?'I always

00:37:50.920 --> 00:37:52.310
say, 'What's your five-year plan? What's

00:37:52.320 --> 00:37:54.430
your 10-year

00:37:54.430 --> 00:37:54.440
goal?'If

00:37:54.440 --> 00:37:56.710
the Lord carries, where will I be by

00:37:56.720 --> 00:37:59.590
the time I'm such and such age, 50

00:37:59.590 --> 00:37:59.600
or 60

00:37:59.600 --> 00:38:01.350
years old, whatever? What do you want

00:38:01.360 --> 00:38:03.270
to do? Because I had a

00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:05.630
dream to get here to pray and do

00:38:05.640 --> 00:38:07.750
what God's called me to do,

00:38:07.760 --> 00:38:10.470
but it took years. As I was praying

00:38:10.480 --> 00:38:11.830
this morning,

00:38:11.840 --> 00:38:14.150
he said, 'You don't realize all the

00:38:14.160 --> 00:38:15.670
years that you were on the back side of

00:38:15.680 --> 00:38:17.390
the desert as a janitor at that

00:38:17.400 --> 00:38:18.590
church,

00:38:18.600 --> 00:38:21.150
being a janitor at that

00:38:21.150 --> 00:38:21.160
mega-ministry,

00:38:21.160 --> 00:38:22.950
being a janitor here and doing what I've

00:38:22.960 --> 00:38:25.110
called you to do. I was growing great

00:38:25.120 --> 00:38:28.630
taproots with

00:38:28.630 --> 00:38:28.640
you.'I

00:38:28.640 --> 00:38:30.390
said, 'What do you

00:38:30.390 --> 00:38:30.400
mean?'He

00:38:30.400 --> 00:38:32.270
said, 'You're freaking out

00:38:32.280 --> 00:38:34.590
because of all the fruit and all that

00:38:34.600 --> 00:38:35.870
I've done and how everything has

00:38:35.880 --> 00:38:38.390
happened so quickly, but it took years

00:38:38.400 --> 00:38:41.910
of cultivation that nobody saw.

00:38:41.920 --> 00:38:44.110
There were great roots that I've had

00:38:44.120 --> 00:38:46.790
growing way down deep. The

00:38:46.800 --> 00:38:49.230
greater the root, the greater the growth

00:38:49.240 --> 00:38:51.950
of the tree can be to sustain it because

00:38:51.960 --> 00:38:54.670
a strong wind can't blow over a

00:38:54.680 --> 00:38:57.990
tree that has great

00:38:57.990 --> 00:38:58.000
roots.'And

00:38:58.000 --> 00:38:59.630
he said just because you didn't

00:38:59.640 --> 00:39:02.030
see the outward growth doesn't mean I

00:39:02.040 --> 00:39:03.790
wasn't growing a deep taproot with you,

00:39:03.800 --> 00:39:06.190
Brandon and Diana.

00:39:06.200 --> 00:39:08.510
He said, 'Don't underestimate the

00:39:08.520 --> 00:39:10.830
20-some years I had you being a

00:39:10.830 --> 00:39:10.840
