00:50:03.280 --> 00:50:06.190
Some cities would not have power

00:50:06.200 --> 00:50:08.670
for over a month. And it was so bad they

00:50:08.680 --> 00:50:10.470
weren't able to do

00:50:10.480 --> 00:50:13.430
banking like they wanted to. Chase, I

00:50:13.440 --> 00:50:15.790
saw certain banks completely closed. I

00:50:15.800 --> 00:50:18.630
saw stock markets not working.

00:50:18.640 --> 00:50:23.030
It was major craziness

00:50:23.040 --> 00:50:24.990
and it was hot outside.

00:50:25.000 --> 00:50:27.430
I remember people were very hot, but

00:50:27.440 --> 00:50:29.710
they were shining the lights on the

00:50:29.720 --> 00:50:32.990
buildings, even downtown New York,

00:50:33.000 --> 00:50:35.270
keeping the lights with emergency

00:50:35.270 --> 00:50:35.280
lighting,

00:50:35.280 --> 00:50:37.870
trying to have reflection for it to have

00:50:37.880 --> 00:50:38.550
a

00:50:38.560 --> 00:50:41.030
source of light on glass-front,

00:50:41.030 --> 00:50:41.040
mirrored-front

00:50:41.040 --> 00:50:43.190
buildings,

00:50:43.200 --> 00:50:45.590
trying to put spotlights to shine off of

00:50:45.600 --> 00:50:47.950
them to bounce it to make light.

00:50:47.960 --> 00:50:49.550
I saw this,

00:50:49.560 --> 00:50:52.230
but as I was watching the train going

00:50:52.240 --> 00:50:54.670
through that had some kind of device

00:50:54.680 --> 00:50:57.750
like in Ocean's Eleven that would send forth

00:50:57.760 --> 00:51:00.630
a pulse into these substations to knock

00:51:00.640 --> 00:51:03.350
and fry them out with some kind of

00:51:03.360 --> 00:51:05.550
electric

00:51:07.520 --> 00:51:08.830
weapon.

00:51:08.840 --> 00:51:10.430
I don't know what this was,

00:51:10.440 --> 00:51:13.630
but it was in the back of a boxcar going

00:51:13.640 --> 00:51:18.230
down the railroad tracks as it would go

00:51:18.240 --> 00:51:20.350
and it would only go off whenever it was

00:51:22.600 --> 00:51:23.950
told to.

00:51:23.960 --> 00:51:25.790
So it would go through a major city

00:51:25.800 --> 00:51:27.950
and it would keep going.

00:51:27.960 --> 00:51:29.870
Does that make sense?

00:51:29.880 --> 00:51:32.230
And so the Lord said, 'Pray over your

00:51:32.240 --> 00:51:35.190
gas plants, your

00:51:35.200 --> 00:51:37.550
oil plants,

00:51:37.560 --> 00:51:39.110
Tuttle, Oklahoma,

00:51:39.120 --> 00:51:40.550
Houston area,

00:51:40.560 --> 00:51:43.110
Louisiana, so on and so

00:51:43.110 --> 00:51:43.120
on.'Every

00:51:43.120 --> 00:51:45.710
place that has a major oil

00:51:45.720 --> 00:51:49.670
rig or gas rigs, pray over the Gulf. I saw

00:51:49.670 --> 00:51:49.680
a

00:51:49.680 --> 00:51:52.190
BP

00:51:52.200 --> 00:51:55.710
oil spill again—another kind of a BP

00:51:55.720 --> 00:51:58.270
oil spill trying to come forth in the

00:51:58.280 --> 00:52:00.750
Gulf of America.

00:52:02.240 --> 00:52:04.150
This is very serious.

00:52:04.160 --> 00:52:05.790
I could see

00:52:05.790 --> 00:52:05.800
saboteurs

00:52:05.800 --> 00:52:09.510
trying to sabotage oil rigs in the Gulf,

00:52:09.520 --> 00:52:12.470
those huge platform

00:52:12.480 --> 00:52:17.310
oil rigs, trying to mess them up somehow.

00:52:19.320 --> 00:52:22.070
I saw drones. Continue

00:52:22.080 --> 00:52:24.470
to pray about the drones, using drones

00:52:24.480 --> 00:52:25.750
against

00:52:25.760 --> 00:52:29.070
baseball stadiums like

00:52:29.070 --> 00:52:29.080
the

00:52:29.080 --> 00:52:32.390
New York Yankees.

00:52:32.390 --> 00:52:32.400
Pray

00:52:32.400 --> 00:52:34.550
for

00:52:34.560 --> 00:52:37.470
drones in baseball stadiums. If you see

00:52:37.480 --> 00:52:40.430
drones flying close down and it feels

00:52:40.440 --> 00:52:44.110
weird and you're at a game, get up

00:52:44.120 --> 00:52:45.990
until you know if there's safety.

00:52:46.000 --> 00:52:47.830
I saw it being landed down with some

00:52:47.840 --> 00:52:49.870
kind of explosive device and being set

00:52:49.880 --> 00:52:51.430
off in these

00:52:51.440 --> 00:52:53.550
stadiums. And the Lord said, 'You must

00:52:53.560 --> 00:52:55.910
pray for this stuff.

00:52:55.920 --> 00:53:00.150
These people are

00:53:00.150 --> 00:53:00.160
sick.'And

00:53:00.160 --> 00:53:01.110
that's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:53:01.120 --> 00:53:03.270
Pray over the race, the marathons on the

00:53:03.280 --> 00:53:06.590
20th in Boston. Pray over the marathons.

00:53:06.600 --> 00:53:09.870
Pray over mass gatherings.

00:53:09.880 --> 00:53:12.350
We prayed over the churches for Easter

00:53:12.360 --> 00:53:14.310
and we had great success.

00:53:14.320 --> 00:53:16.670
Now our job is not done.

00:53:16.680 --> 00:53:18.390
The Lord is calling us to pray for

00:53:18.400 --> 00:53:21.030
major gatherings, like

00:53:21.040 --> 00:53:22.910
Coachella.

00:53:22.920 --> 00:53:24.430
Pray

00:53:24.440 --> 00:53:27.270
for Coachella.

00:53:27.280 --> 00:53:29.390
That comes in a couple of months

00:53:29.400 --> 00:53:31.630
or next month or this month.

00:53:38.040 --> 00:53:40.230
A lot of people go to these places that

00:53:40.230 --> 00:53:40.240
are

00:53:40.240 --> 00:53:45.470
not sober.

00:53:45.480 --> 00:53:47.950
Play this.

00:53:47.960 --> 00:53:51.630
This is last year, March 23rd of

00:53:51.640 --> 00:53:54.150
2025.

00:53:54.160 --> 00:53:56.310
Ready? Go ahead.

00:53:56.320 --> 00:53:58.390
'You're going to turn it around for good,

00:53:58.400 --> 00:53:59.990
Father, for they're on both

00:53:59.990 --> 00:54:00.000
sides.'They're

00:54:00.000 --> 00:54:01.670
on both

00:54:01.680 --> 00:54:02.790
sides.

00:54:02.800 --> 00:54:06.150
But there's a mole within.

00:54:06.160 --> 00:54:08.110
There's a mole again. And I see a mole in

00:54:08.120 --> 00:54:11.550
our own facility and a mole in

00:54:12.840 --> 00:54:15.710
our own government.

00:54:15.720 --> 00:54:18.550
I see one person,

00:54:18.550 --> 00:54:18.560
and

00:54:18.560 --> 00:54:21.070
they are

00:54:21.080 --> 00:54:24.590
trying to do this secretly. They try to

00:54:24.600 --> 00:54:26.830
devise the plans of what we're

00:54:26.840 --> 00:54:34.070
trying to do secretly.

00:54:34.070 --> 00:54:34.080
We

00:54:34.080 --> 00:54:36.790
call this

00:54:36.800 --> 00:54:40.070
mole found; we call

00:54:40.080 --> 00:54:42.510
the mole uncovered. We say in the name

00:54:42.520 --> 00:54:45.310
of Jesus, 'You are

00:54:45.310 --> 00:54:45.320
uncovered.'Even

00:54:45.320 --> 00:54:47.470
after work,

00:54:47.480 --> 00:54:50.070
when they get off, they

00:54:50.070 --> 00:54:50.080
are

00:54:50.080 --> 00:54:52.350
trying to communicate

00:54:52.360 --> 00:54:54.430
in a way that will not get them

00:54:54.440 --> 00:54:55.950
caught through

00:54:57.080 --> 00:54:59.710
an avenue of hidden

00:54:59.720 --> 00:55:02.350
communication.

00:55:02.360 --> 00:55:05.150
It's almost a deciphered

00:55:05.150 --> 00:55:05.160
code—only

00:55:05.160 --> 00:55:07.310
they would know how to use certain

00:55:07.320 --> 00:55:09.950
words with certain letters.

00:55:09.960 --> 00:55:12.390
They're like numbered.

00:55:12.400 --> 00:55:14.550
It's not family they're

00:55:14.560 --> 00:55:16.470
talking to. It goes from

00:55:16.480 --> 00:55:18.310
telephone to telephone,

00:55:20.680 --> 00:55:23.310
relayed

00:55:25.280 --> 00:55:28.790
twice: one and then

00:55:28.800 --> 00:55:32.030
another. It goes

00:55:32.040 --> 00:55:36.190
deeper; it's a deep trail.

00:55:36.200 --> 00:55:38.470
It's not directly to them; it goes from

00:55:38.480 --> 00:55:40.550
here to here to here.

00:55:40.560 --> 00:55:44.190
It's twice: one and then there.

00:55:44.200 --> 00:55:46.190
I see it; this is well

00:55:49.800 --> 00:56:06.910
thought out.

00:56:06.920 --> 00:56:09.150
We pray over our servicemen and women in

00:56:09.160 --> 00:56:10.630
Iraq.

00:56:10.640 --> 00:56:14.790
We pray for our bases in Iraq. We pray a

00:56:14.800 --> 00:56:18.150
hedge of blood around and about them

00:56:18.160 --> 00:56:21.750
right now from any surprise attack.

00:56:21.760 --> 00:56:24.750
We pray

00:56:24.760 --> 00:56:26.630
a hedge around and about our servicemen

00:56:26.640 --> 00:56:29.230
and women in the name of Jesus that no

00:56:29.240 --> 00:56:31.470
weapon formed against them would prosper.

00:56:31.480 --> 00:56:33.870
Every tongue that rises against them, we

00:56:33.880 --> 00:56:35.910
condemn it; we command it in the name of

00:56:35.920 --> 00:56:38.790
Jesus to bow its knee.

00:56:38.800 --> 00:56:41.670
We pray

00:56:41.680 --> 00:56:44.670
a hedge of blood around Iraq. We pray

00:56:44.680 --> 00:56:47.190
for wisdom for Trump making these

00:56:47.200 --> 00:56:48.950
decisions ahead.

00:56:48.960 --> 00:56:54.230
It's like a chess match.

00:56:54.240 --> 00:56:56.510
He needs wisdom; we pray for wisdom for

00:56:56.520 --> 00:56:58.550
his mind. We pray for the people

00:56:58.560 --> 00:57:00.430
around him not to think with a

00:57:00.440 --> 00:57:02.870
reprobate mind. We pray a hedge around

00:57:02.880 --> 00:57:04.910
his mind. We thank you, Lord,

00:57:04.920 --> 00:57:07.350
that he

00:57:07.360 --> 00:57:09.630
thinks through you to a higher level

00:57:09.640 --> 00:57:12.110
than he's ever thought before.

00:57:12.110 --> 00:57:12.120
Because

00:57:12.120 --> 00:57:14.270
he has

00:57:14.270 --> 00:57:14.280
to

00:57:14.280 --> 00:57:16.630
make

00:57:16.640 --> 00:57:19.830
the right choice,

00:57:23.320 --> 00:57:25.430
this choice will turn out a new

00:57:25.440 --> 00:57:26.830
outcome.

00:57:30.560 --> 00:57:32.790
He has to see

00:57:32.800 --> 00:57:36.390
like chess,

00:57:36.400 --> 00:57:38.190
how many steps ahead. It's not just one

00:57:38.200 --> 00:57:40.750
move; it's seeing the other moves before

00:57:40.760 --> 00:57:42.790
he needs to move it.

00:57:42.800 --> 00:57:46.230
What will this do if you make this

00:57:46.240 --> 00:57:47.310
one,

00:57:47.320 --> 00:57:49.710
so that you're always ahead?

00:57:49.720 --> 00:57:51.870
It's not just playing

00:57:51.880 --> 00:57:53.830
one position at a time; it's playing

00:57:53.840 --> 00:57:55.750
five positions at a time.

00:57:55.760 --> 00:57:58.390
I see him; he needs to make strategic

00:57:58.400 --> 00:58:01.190
plans.

00:58:01.200 --> 00:58:03.510
He's running them

00:58:03.520 --> 00:58:06.230
through his mind right now,

00:58:06.240 --> 00:58:08.870
measuring each plan

00:58:08.870 --> 00:58:08.880
and

00:58:08.880 --> 00:58:11.790
decision.

00:58:14.120 --> 00:58:17.230
But he needs not his plan, but the Holy

00:58:17.230 --> 00:58:17.240
Ghost's

00:58:17.240 --> 00:58:20.110
plan. So we pray for his mind

00:58:20.110 --> 00:58:20.120
and

00:58:20.120 --> 00:58:22.910
for his spirit to catch it.

00:58:22.920 --> 00:58:25.070
We catch it right now in the name of

00:58:25.080 --> 00:58:27.310
Jesus out of the realm of the spirit,

00:58:27.320 --> 00:58:29.430
and we pull it to him. We catch

00:58:29.440 --> 00:58:31.510
it for him and for the body of

00:58:31.520 --> 00:58:33.150
Christ. He may not know how to pray

00:58:33.160 --> 00:58:35.190
through it, but we pray it. We bring it

00:58:35.200 --> 00:58:37.270
forth in the name of Jesus:

00:58:37.280 --> 00:58:41.070
the divine plan

00:58:41.080 --> 00:58:43.390
of knowing what to do to make the step

00:58:43.400 --> 00:58:45.550
to go right through. Not just what we

00:58:45.560 --> 00:58:47.990
think is right in our own mind, but what

00:58:48.000 --> 00:58:49.590
is right by what the hand of the

00:58:49.600 --> 00:58:52.070
Lord says and what the voice of the Lord

00:58:52.080 --> 00:58:54.310
would say. We call it forth in the name

00:58:54.320 --> 00:58:56.470
of Jesus.

00:58:56.470 --> 00:58:56.480
They're

00:58:56.480 --> 00:59:00.030
trying to poke the beehive;

00:59:00.040 --> 00:59:01.510
that's what they're going to do.

00:59:01.520 --> 00:59:03.470
They

00:59:03.480 --> 00:59:05.790
try to stir it up over here. sleight of hand, folks; I see it. They want to

00:59:05.800 --> 00:59:08.070
stir it up over here

00:59:12.320 --> 00:59:14.270
to keep you

00:59:14.280 --> 00:59:15.950
occupied

00:59:15.960 --> 00:59:18.470
while

00:59:18.480 --> 00:59:20.710
hiding in the mountains.

00:59:20.720 --> 00:59:23.670
We call those

00:59:27.120 --> 00:59:29.670
hostages

00:59:29.680 --> 00:59:32.670
released. If there's any more alive,

00:59:35.000 --> 00:59:38.270
we call the hostages released.

00:59:38.280 --> 00:59:40.390
We take authority over this demonic

00:59:40.400 --> 00:59:43.910
spirit that tries to rule over this area

00:59:43.910 --> 00:59:43.920
and

00:59:43.920 --> 00:59:46.390
kill these people.

00:59:49.480 --> 00:59:51.510
Father, we thank you.

00:59:51.520 --> 00:59:53.830
The very

00:59:53.840 --> 00:59:57.870
pit they dug, the very trap they've

00:59:59.110 --> 00:59:59.120
dug—this

01:00:00.840 --> 01:00:01.950
is the only leverage they have

01:00:01.960 --> 01:00:03.510
anymore.

01:00:03.520 --> 01:00:06.350
They can't give away all their

01:00:06.350 --> 01:00:06.360
cards;

01:00:06.360 --> 01:00:10.110
they can't reveal all their

01:00:10.110 --> 01:00:10.120
cards.

01:00:10.120 --> 01:00:11.470
It's amazing; there's

01:00:11.470 --> 01:00:11.480
so much

01:00:11.480 --> 01:00:12.990
here.

01:00:13.000 --> 01:00:14.990
This is not just a

01:00:15.000 --> 01:00:17.270
one-time project. The Lord

01:00:17.270 --> 01:00:17.280
says,

01:00:17.280 --> 01:00:18.910
'Listen to that

01:00:23.630 --> 01:00:23.640
again.'Many

01:00:25.000 --> 01:00:26.670
days over

01:00:26.670 --> 01:00:26.680
this leak,

01:00:26.680 --> 01:00:28.470
many days of

01:00:28.480 --> 01:00:35.990
prayer.

01:00:36.000 --> 01:00:38.830
Praying over the

01:00:38.830 --> 01:00:38.840
leaker

01:00:38.840 --> 01:00:41.870
because

01:00:41.880 --> 01:00:44.430
that's a sick person

01:00:44.430 --> 01:00:44.440
who

01:00:44.440 --> 01:00:46.430
probably didn't realize the extent of

01:00:46.440 --> 01:00:48.590
how bad it was.

01:00:50.680 --> 01:00:53.110
It's national security, and

01:00:53.120 --> 01:00:55.950
the person that did the story

01:00:55.960 --> 01:00:58.350
will go to jail if he doesn't say.

01:00:59.880 --> 01:01:01.350
They put

01:01:01.360 --> 01:01:03.510
this mission at great risk, they put

01:01:03.520 --> 01:01:05.230
that man at great risk, and they put the

01:01:05.240 --> 01:01:07.230
hundreds of people that went in looking

01:01:07.240 --> 01:01:09.190
for him at risk. There's a leak because everyone now

01:01:09.200 --> 01:01:12.630
knows that we're going in.

01:01:12.640 --> 01:01:13.550
When I was looking into

01:01:14.680 --> 01:01:16.070
that back in

01:01:16.080 --> 01:01:18.910
March of last year,

01:01:18.910 --> 01:01:18.920
the

01:01:18.920 --> 01:01:20.110
Lord

01:01:20.110 --> 01:01:20.120
was

01:01:20.120 --> 01:01:21.390
showing me

01:01:21.400 --> 01:01:24.030
something in great detail.

01:01:27.760 --> 01:01:30.470
I saw military men and women.

01:01:30.480 --> 01:01:32.310
The Lord said, 'Pray for these people;

01:01:32.320 --> 01:01:34.070
they're in danger,

01:01:34.080 --> 01:01:36.190
for the leak will cause these people to

01:01:36.200 --> 01:01:38.430
be in

01:01:38.430 --> 01:01:38.440
danger.'That's

01:01:38.440 --> 01:01:40.790
why I said

01:01:40.790 --> 01:01:40.800
to

01:01:40.800 --> 01:01:43.030
pray over the bases.

01:01:43.040 --> 01:01:45.310
Back in March of last year, there was no

01:01:45.320 --> 01:01:46.390
reason to.

01:01:49.160 --> 01:01:50.870
The Lord said, 'Pray over these bases;

01:01:50.880 --> 01:01:53.070
it's bigger than just this

01:01:53.080 --> 01:01:55.110
rescue

01:01:55.120 --> 01:01:58.030
mission.'God

01:01:58.040 --> 01:02:00.710
was giving us something

01:02:00.720 --> 01:02:03.830
a year in advance.

01:02:03.840 --> 01:02:07.470
We

01:02:07.480 --> 01:02:08.950
see

01:02:08.960 --> 01:02:11.870
in the future

01:02:11.880 --> 01:02:14.190
to tell you

01:02:14.190 --> 01:02:14.200
that

01:02:14.200 --> 01:02:16.270
you must pray over the bases in the

01:02:16.280 --> 01:02:17.990
Middle East.

01:02:18.000 --> 01:02:20.390
Why? In March of last year, that

01:02:20.390 --> 01:02:20.400
didn't

01:02:20.400 --> 01:02:22.310
make sense, did it?

01:02:22.320 --> 01:02:23.510
Most people were going, 'Why pray over

01:02:25.400 --> 01:02:26.990
the?'I

01:02:28.560 --> 01:02:31.430
said, 'A major war; I've seen

01:02:31.430 --> 01:02:31.440
it.'But

01:02:31.440 --> 01:02:37.990
there's a leak; there is a rat.

01:02:42.160 --> 01:02:43.630
I believe with all my heart He's

01:02:43.640 --> 01:02:44.870
going to lead us and we're going to

01:02:44.880 --> 01:02:47.830
uncover the rat.

01:02:47.840 --> 01:02:49.990
We're going to expose the mole.

01:03:00.160 --> 01:03:02.270
Father, we just thank you

01:03:02.280 --> 01:03:04.310
for the body.

01:03:06.800 --> 01:03:08.590
We never come into this river of prayer

01:03:08.600 --> 01:03:11.790
without taking communion first.

01:03:11.800 --> 01:03:13.190
We're so grateful for

01:03:13.200 --> 01:03:15.150
accuracy and that you

01:03:15.160 --> 01:03:17.590
tell us that which is to come.

01:03:17.600 --> 01:03:19.710
We're being used

01:03:19.720 --> 01:03:21.590
for the kingdom for such a

01:03:21.600 --> 01:03:23.550
time as this.

01:03:23.560 --> 01:03:25.510
Father, we keep ourselves right

01:03:25.520 --> 01:03:27.510
before you and you show us the secret

01:03:27.520 --> 01:03:29.750
hidden things.

01:03:29.760 --> 01:03:31.350
We lift up this body right

01:03:31.360 --> 01:03:34.030
now in the name of Jesus, and we give you

01:03:34.040 --> 01:03:37.110
all the glory, honor, and praise.

01:03:47.760 --> 01:03:49.550
We plead the blood;

